# Docs and tickets

- Update `LIVE_FACTS.json` and `docs/operations/live-environment.md` together
  after an approved live-state change.
- Run the document-link and ticket-parity checks before committing.
- Binding reviews under `docs/reviews/<DDMMYY>/` outrank earlier written
  requirements in the areas they cover.
- Ticket frontmatter and status folders are authoritative. BOARD, indexes, and
  plan progress are generated; do not hand-maintain them.
- Install the repository hooks with `git config core.hooksPath scripts/hooks`.
